Published: 01 May 2026

Distributional effects of expanding climate targets beyond CO2
                    Yating Kang 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0009-0001-7880-96811,2,3 na1, Peipei Tian 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0003-0465-40982 na1, Laixiang Sun 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0002-7784-79424,5, Xiangjie Chen 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0002-4884-25874, Yuru Guan 
            ORCID: orcid.org/0000-0003-4426-70176,7, Kuishuang Feng 
